                  </div>
                  <div class="grid gap-1">
                      <dt class="text-sm font-semibold text-foreground">Address</dt>
                      <dd>Floridablanca, Santander, Colombia</dd>
                  </div>
                  <div class="grid gap-1">
                      <dt class="text-sm font-semibold text-foreground">Phone</dt>
                      <dd>+57 310 785 1074</dd>
                  </div>
                  <div class="grid gap-1">
                      <dt class="text-sm font-semibold text-foreground">Email</dt>
                      <dd>joseomarfernandez747@gmail.com</dd>
                  </div>
              </dl>
          </div>
      </section>

      <!-- 2. Definitions -->
      <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">2. Definitions</h2>
          <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground list-disc">
              <li><span class="font-semibold text-foreground">"We", "our":</span> Refers to Jose Omar Fernandez Fuentes</li>
              <li><span class="font-semibold text-foreground">"You", "client":</span> Refers to the user of this website or service contractor</li>
              <li><span class="font-semibold text-foreground">"Services":</span> Web design, web development, SEO, programming, and related services</li>
              <li><span class="font-semibold text-foreground">"Website":</span> This website and all its content</li>
              <li><span class="font-semibold text-foreground">"Project":</span> Specific work agreed between the client and service provider</li>
          </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- 3. Services Offered -->
      <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">3. Services Offered</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-8 mb-6">We offer the following professional services:</p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">3.1 Web Design and Development</h3>
          <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground list-disc">
              <li>Responsive website design</li>
              <li>Web application development</li>
              <li>User interface design (UI/UX)</li>
              <li>HTML/CSS layout</li>
              <li>Development with modern frameworks (React, Next.js, etc.)</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">3.2 SEO Optimization</h3>
          <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground list-disc">
              <li>Technical SEO</li>
              <li>On-page optimization</li>
              <li>Keyword analysis</li>
              <li>Web performance improvement</li>
              <li>Content strategies</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">3.3 Programming and Development</h3>
          <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground list-disc">
              <li>Frontend and backend development</li>
              <li>API integration</li>
              <li>Custom functionality development</li>
              <li>Maintenance and technical support</li>
          </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- 4. Hiring Process -->
      <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">4. Hiring Process</h2>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">4.1 Quote Request</h3>
          <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground list-disc">
              <li>The client requests a quote detailing their needs</li>
              <li>We provide a quote within 48-72 business hours</li>
              <li>The quote is valid for 30 calendar days</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">4.2 Quote Acceptance</h3>
          <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground list-disc">
              <li>The client accepts the quote via written confirmation (email)</li>
              <li>A specific service contract or agreement is signed</li>
              <li>A work schedule and deliverables are established</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">4.3 Project Start</h3>
          <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground list-disc">
              <li>The project starts after receiving the agreed initial payment</li>
              <li>Specific delivery deadlines are assigned</li>
              <li>Communication channels are established</li>
          </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- 5. Commercial Terms -->
      <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">5. Commercial Terms</h2>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">5.1 Prices and Payments</h3>
          <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground list-disc">
              <li>All prices are expressed in Colombian Pesos (COP) or US Dollars (USD)</li>
              <li>Prices do not include VAT (19%) unless specified otherwise</li>
              <li>Accepted payment methods: Bank transfer, Nequi / Daviplata, PayPal (international projects), others by agreement</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">5.2 Payment Structure</h3>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-black/5 dark:border-white/10 bg-black/5 dark:bg-white/5 p-6 mb-6">
              <p class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-4">Standard projects:</p>
              <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground list-disc">
                  <li>50% advance at project start</li>
                  <li>50% remaining upon project completion and delivery</li>
              </ul>

              <p class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-4 mt-6">Large projects (over $5,000,000 COP):</p>
              <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground list-disc">
                  <li>40% advance</li>
                  <li>30% at 50% progress</li>
                  <li>30% upon completion</li>
              </ul>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">5.3 Payment Deadlines</h3>
          <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground list-disc">
              <li>Invoices must be paid within 5 business days after issuance</li>
              <li>Payment delays may result in project suspension</li>
              <li>Late payments over 15 days may generate late interest of 1.5% monthly</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">5.4 Refunds</h3>
          <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground list-disc">
              <li>No refunds are made once the project has started</li>
              <li>If the client cancels before start, 100% of the advance is refunded</li>
              <li>Cancellations after start: work completed according to progress is charged</li>
          </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- 6. Intellectual Property and Copyright -->
      <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">6. Intellectual Property and Copyright</h2>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">6.1 Client Ownership</h3>
