              Upon complete payment, the client obtains full usage rights of the final delivered design, project source code,
              design files (if applicable), and necessary licenses for website operation.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">6.2 Rights Reserved by Provider</h3>
          <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground list-disc">
              <li>Include the project in our portfolio</li>
              <li>Use screenshots in marketing materials</li>
              <li>Mention the project as a reference (unless confidentiality agreement)</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">6.3 Third-Party Code and Frameworks</h3>
          <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground list-disc">
              <li>Open-source frameworks maintain their original licenses</li>
              <li>Third-party libraries are governed by their respective licenses</li>
              <li>Client will be notified of any specific license dependencies</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">6.4 Client Content</h3>
          <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground list-disc">
              <li>The client retains all rights to content they provide</li>
              <li>The client guarantees having rights to all supplied material</li>
              <li>The client is responsible for any copyright infringement</li>
          </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- 7. Client Responsibilities -->
      <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">7. Client Responsibilities</h2>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">7.1 Material Provision</h3>
