              <li>Ensure having rights to all provided material</li>
              <li>Review and approve deliverables within agreed deadlines</li>
              <li>Provide clear and constructive feedback</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">7.2 Access and Credentials</h3>
          <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground list-disc">
              <li>Provide necessary access (hosting, domain, APIs)</li>
              <li>Maintain security of their own credentials</li>
              <li>Inform any changes in access or platforms</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">7.3 Communication</h3>
          <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground list-disc">
              <li>Maintain active communication during the project</li>
              <li>Respond to inquiries within a reasonable time (maximum 72 hours)</li>
              <li>Designate a single point of contact if an organization</li>
          </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- 8. Our Responsibilities and Guarantees -->
      <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">8. Our Responsibilities and Guarantees</h2>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">8.1 Commitments</h3>
          <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground list-disc">
              <li>Deliver professional quality work</li>
              <li>Meet agreed deadlines (except for force majeure causes)</li>
              <li>Maintain clear and regular communication</li>
              <li>Protect project confidentiality</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">8.2 Functionality Guarantee</h3>
          <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground list-disc">
              <li>We guarantee correct website operation for 30 days post-delivery</li>
              <li>We correct programming errors at no additional cost during this period</li>
              <li>Guarantee does not cover scope changes or new functionalities</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">8.3 Limitations</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-8 mb-4">We do not guarantee:</p>
          <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground list-disc">
              <li>Specific search engine rankings</li>
              <li>Specific web traffic or conversions</li>
              <li>Compatibility with obsolete or discontinued browsers</li>
              <li>Operation with unagreed third-party plugins or themes</li>
