          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">9. Modifications and Scope Changes</h2>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">9.1 Minor Changes</h3>
          <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground list-disc">
              <li>Minor adjustments within agreed scope are included</li>
              <li>Up to 2 rounds of revisions are allowed at no additional cost</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">9.2 Significant Changes</h3>
          <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground list-disc">
              <li>Changes that alter original scope require additional quotation</li>
              <li>Project will be paused until additional cost is approved and agreed</li>
              <li>Delivery deadlines will be adjusted according to requested changes</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">9.3 Change Orders</h3>
