              <li>All significant changes will be documented in writing</li>
              <li>Explicit approval will be required before proceeding</li>
              <li>Additional costs and times will be communicated before execution</li>
          </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- 10. Deadlines and Deliveries -->
      <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">10. Deadlines and Deliveries</h2>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">10.1 Schedule</h3>
          <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground list-disc">
              <li>A schedule is established at project start</li>
              <li>Deadlines depend on project complexity and scope</li>
              <li>Client delays in providing materials extend deadlines</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">10.2 Final Delivery</h3>
          <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground list-disc">
              <li>Client is notified when the project is ready</li>
              <li>Client has 7 days for final review</li>
              <li>Official delivery proceeds after approval and final payment</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">10.3 Force Majeure</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-8">Deadlines may be extended by events beyond our control, emergencies, third-party technical issues, or natural disasters.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- 11. Confidentiality -->
