              <li>Maintain confidentiality of all client sensitive information</li>
              <li>Not disclose commercial or strategic details</li>
              <li>Protect provided credentials and access</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">11.2 Exceptions</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-8">Information that is public, legally obtained from third parties, or required by law is not considered confidential.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- 12. Contract Termination -->
      <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">12. Contract Termination</h2>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">12.1 Termination by Client</h3>
          <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground list-disc">
              <li>You can cancel the project with 7 days written notice</li>
              <li>Work completed to date will be billed</li>
              <li>No refund of advance if work has already started</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">12.2 Termination by Provider</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-8">We may terminate the contract if there are payment defaults, lack of materials, abusive conduct, or fraudulent/illegal activity.</p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">12.3 Delivery upon Termination</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-8">Work completed to date is delivered; client must pay for work performed and source files are not delivered without full payment.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- 13. Limitation of Liability -->
      <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">13. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-8 mb-6">
              Our liability is limited to the total amount paid by the client for the specific project and to error correction within the warranty period.
