          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">14.2 Additional Services</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-8">Can be contracted separately: monthly maintenance, content updates, new functionalities, extended support, hosting and domain.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- 15. Hosting and Domain -->
      <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">15. Hosting and Domain</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-8">The client is responsible for contracting hosting and domain. We can advise or offer management (additional cost).</p>
      </section>

      <!-- 16. Acceptable Use -->
      <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">16. Acceptable Use</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-8 mb-4">We will not develop projects that promote illegal content, violate rights, promote hate/violence, or facilitate fraudulent activities.</p>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-8">We reserve the right to reject or terminate projects that violate these principles.</p>
