      <!-- 17. Dispute Resolution -->
      <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">17. Dispute Resolution</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-8 mb-4">We will attempt to resolve disputes through direct communication. If unsuccessful, professional mediation can be sought (costs 50/50).</p>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-8">These terms are governed by Colombian laws and jurisdiction in Bucaramanga, Santander, Colombia.</p>
